reviewText: I love it I hope you have it soon in sock I want to buy it?
There's a full episode was missing from the original air cast, when they all go on vacation to Acapulco. Other than that it was good.
I'm sorry but the comment by Ana is incorrect.  There's no way you could've seen this back in the 80's when it originally aired in 1990/1991.
I got the video very promptly and as promised. The novela made a huge impact in my life. I love that eventhough its edited , so far I'm pleased with the content.

I have been looking for these for a long time as well. I really enjoyed the videos, except that I was really looking for the whole series. It was worth it though. It is something to buy if u just want some kind of memory of the novela. I do suggest to buy it for that purpose. But if you are looking for something really good and if you want a lot of what you saw on the tv then i suggest you look somewhere else.

I really enjoyed it. I am gald I purchase it. I had been looking for this telenovela for years. I saw it back in the 80's. The seller was great the item was new as described and I received it as promised on time. I give the seller a hi 5.
